videos.description: Virginia's Mamadi Diakite comes up with a nice block to set up a Braxton Key jam on the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Key gets in the paint for powerful UVa slam) 2020/1/7

videos.headline: Key gets in the paint for powerful UVa slam

videos.description: CJ Felder drives through multiple Virginia defenders on his way to the hoop, where he shows nice body control and gets a layup to fall.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Felder goes up-and-under for slick BC layup) 2020/1/7

videos.headline: Felder goes up-and-under for slick BC layup

videos.description: Kody Stattmann evades his defender with a nifty behind-the-back dribble then spins on another pair of BC defenders as he drives to the hoop for two.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Stattmann shows off his handles as UVa fights back) 2020/1/7

videos.headline: Stattmann shows off his handles as UVa fights back

videos.description: Kihei Clark pulls up for a deep 3-pointer to knot the game at 45-45. On the next possession, he takes advantage of a BC turnover as he dishes a nice pass to Mamadi Diakite in transition for a go-ahead layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Virginia's Clark, Diakite team up for clutch sequence) 2020/1/7

videos.headline: Virginia's Clark, Diakite team up for clutch sequence
